headline: Jacobs' Board Approves $1.5 Billion Share Repurchase Authorization
summary: The Jacobs' (NYSE: J) Board of Directors has approved a new incremental share repurchase authorization (the "2025 Share Repurchase Program"). The 2025 Share Repurchase Program authorizes the purchase of up to $1.5 billion of Jacobs' common stock over a three-year period.
